{"tid":1578751,"cid":5,"subCid":12,"title":"先旨聲明：邊個區議員今晚夠膽去林鄭個假對話show, 今年區議會選舉將會一票不投此人","createTime":"2019-09-18T09:02:31.000Z","updateTime":"2019-09-18T17:08:03.000Z","uid":66260,"like":27,"dislike":3,"uniUserReply":18,"replies":[{"pid":"20c9e1c3d32f62f770e072aae95922ff0a5d3eb0","tid":1578751,"uid":66260,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2019-09-18T09:02:31.000Z","msg":"民政事務處上周五（13日）向全港區議員發邀請信，邀請區議員於周三（18日）晚上7至9時出席「對話會」，與特首與部分主要官員會面。<br />\n<br />\n原來係今日<img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/smile.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/hehe.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"fcfd074d5fc5b8ec6c7a5edb28b5fc515240d719","tid":1578751,"uid":69334,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-09-18T09:03:09.000Z","msg":"已準備mark低"},{"pid":"0ee132a877c5175ba34cefebb3f4e482b2693b5c","tid":1578751,"uid":117906,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-09-18T09:03:34.000Z","msg":"<strong><span style=\"color: red;\"><span style=\"font-size: x-large;\">全球響應「929全球集會抗赤納粹」</span></span></strong><br />\n<strong><span style=\"color: red;\"><span style=\"font-size: x-large;\">全世界一齊對準極權！</span></span></strong><br />\n<a href=\"https://lih.kg/1577380\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">https://lih.kg/1577380</a><br />\n<img src=\"https://na.cx/i/hWqVmOV.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2FhWqVmOV.jpg&h=075c7745&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<img src=\"https://na.cx/i/n1tov9s.png\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2Fn1tov9s.png&h=0af09f95&s={SIZE}\" />"},{"pid":"3ae029dabed5be4095cc4c8a78a4d7b01f02173f","tid":1578751,"uid":66260,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2019-09-18T09:03:36.000Z","msg":"大家mark實邊個今晚有去<br />\n黎緊選舉一定要幫佢大大力宣傳<img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/clap.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"51371f03bcb2f92b0a70c53c8ce8a77d9d17eb6e","tid":1578751,"uid":117906,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-